# Liabilities Insurance Policy Gross Inwards Reinsurance Amount

## identifier
de4835

## type
float

## definition
Gross Policy Liability in respect of inwards reinsurance business.

This should be the gross figure, not net of retrocessions.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=credit
- name=Liabilities.Insurance.PolicyGrossInwardsReinsurance.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpo/bafpo3.02.04
- period=instant
